Description:
Above & Beyond on the Streetfront!
This one takes street front living to a new level. Master built to an outstanding standard, this three bedroom plus fitted study, 2.5 bathroom, dual zone home goes above and beyond prestige living with an elite Bosch kitchen, fully tiled bathrooms (including a dual vanity ensuite), CaesarStone benchtops (even for the laundry) and a mix of wideboard timber flooring and plush carpets. With all the accoutrements of luxury living, this climate controlled home features ducting vacuum, video intercom entry and an oversize double auto garage with parking in front.
But it's not just the finish that puts this home above all others. Sized up to an extraordinary standard, the home features vast formal and casual living zones, a north facing deck and super sized double bedrooms including master with walk-behind robe... plus more flexible spaces including a study area and a flexible retreat area large enough to fit a small sofa.
Even the location goes above and beyond - just a walk to shops and station with the North Rd and Grange Rd bus services just around the corner.

Secure, serene & surprisingly spacious

Tranquilly set at the rear of a well maintained & secure building, this renovated 1st floor unit has a lively, low maintenance interior where floating floorboards flow from entrance hall into sunlight-flooded open living room with an outlook that feels as if you're living in the trees. The chic kitchen has easy clean cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, & tiled splashback. There are mirror-fronted BIRs; rev-cyc A/C; bathroom/laundry; slimline venetians; carport via automatic gate; & convenience to public transport, recreation & shops.

Attention first home buyers/astute investors!
Own street frontage! Side street access! This could be your opportunity to secure your own slice of the highly sought after McKinnon Secondary College zone. Description:
Decadent In-Zone Lifestyle Living
A masterpiece of unrestrained luxury, this commanding four bedroom plus study family home is sensibly designed & elegantly appointed. Finished to first-class standards with a modern, streamlined kitchen including stainless-steel appliances & CaesarStone work surfaces, free-flowing lounge & dining with bi-fold doors opening out to low maintenance surrounds featuring entertaining decks for the parents, a cubby for the kids, and a family-friendly solar & gas heated in-ground pool! There are 2.5 opulent bathrooms, including a full ensuite to the balconied master; fitted laundry, plush wool carpets & Spotted Gum flooring. Centrally heated, air-conditioned and alarmed with ducted vacuum, water tank and auto double garage, this exceptional home is custom fitted with indoor-outdoor surround-sound, mirrored robes & gas-log fire. A short walk to in-zone McKinnon Secondary College & Primary, Joyce Park and Ormond shops & station, this is sensible lifestyle living wrapped in delightful decadence...

Description:
Classic Californian with Character & Charm!
Pretty as a picture, this street-front Californian Bungalow is an ideal downsizer, investment or first home. Add this character to modern Euro kitchen appliances, reverse-cycle air-conditioning, central heating & attic storage, and you have the perfect blend of charm & convenience! Perfectly positioned beyond picturesque front gardens-walking distance to EE Gunn Reserve, schools, shops & zone 1 station...

Description:
Period Beauty Meets Professional Brilliance!
State-of-the-art style meets family lifestyle in this parkside/off-the-strip location. A fine example of the renovator's art, this four bedroom, 2.5 bathroom period beauty offers an ideal family floorplan featuring a gracious formal lounge, an expansive family zone and more living beyond dual sets of bi-folds in a BBQ-fitted fan-cooled al fresco area. Appointed to an elite standard with a CaesarStone kitchen with elite European appliances including Miele espresso machine, this centrally heated, air-conditioned and alarmed home stars a 5 Star master-domain with fitted dressing area and dual vanity marble ensuite and a frameless-screened main bathroom with the same luxe marble finish. With richly textured Australian hardwood floors reaching out to meet wraparound ironbark decking, this masterpiece renovation is set in artfully landscaped gardens with an aggregate drive leading to carport and a cottage-style garage wired to convert as home-office. With EE Gunn Reserve at one end of the street and Ormond's shopping and transport strip at the other, this is a work of art you can live with!

Description:
Elegant In-Zone Edwardian!
Elegantly Edwardian, this timeless 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom period beauty is rich in character & filled with light. Blending luxurious contemporary amenity with classic architectural styling sees ducted heating, evaporative cooling & alarm alongside high ceilings, rich polished boards, feature leadlight & decorative mantles. Bedrooms (all with robes, master with ensuite) are zoned away from a central formal lounge (OFP), generous separate dining & an open-plan kitchen/family room with stainless-steel appliances, tall windows & external awnings. Designed to maximise the indoor-outdoor connection, with a north-west orientation, wrap-around deck & pretty, private gardens, this charming property is well located walking distance to shops, parks, zone 1 station & in-zone McKinnon Secondary College on 580m2/6250sqft (approx)...

Description:
Comfortable Living with a Family Focus!
Offering a wider-than-usual frontage of 61ft (approx), this 1960s brick veneer has recently been updated to satisfy & please. Three big bedrooms offer built-in-robes...two with reverse cycle air-conditioning, and one with two-way entry...perfect for a new baby or future ensuite. A sunny north-facing lounge & dining (also with air-con) is warmed by rich polished boards & gas heating, whilst the classic kitchen includes a breakfast bar & dishwasher. Set in a quiet, family-friendly street with an appealing streetscape, close to schools, parks, shops & transport, this pretty property includes natural timber architraves, picture rails, new ComfortPlus windows & doors, fresh carpet, 2nd WC, security porch entry, garden shed and a paved entertaining area amongst generous & secure, private rear gardens...
Land 61ft x 99.3ft or 567sqm approx

Description:
House-like Space & a Garden to Love!
Wander down this wide hedged drive, step inside this superior single-level home and find house-like space in easy to love gardens! Stretched out across the rear of a well-groomed group of just three, this big-hearted home offers low-maintenance living with a highly accommodating three bedroom floorplan. Offering light-filled garden-focused living/dining plus more room to dine beside the kitchen, this sizeable home is stylishly renovated with stainless-steel appliances and step-in pantry, a separate shower and bath for the fresh bright bathroom plus a private WC. Centrally heated and air-conditioned with robes for every bedroom, this quality home is even sized up and styled up outside....with an oversize garage plus carspace and generous hedged courtyard offering lawns to run, a sandpit to play and a vegie patch to indulge a green thumb. Located in one of the area's leafiest and loveliest streets within a few blocks of station, bus and shops, this sized up single level is one of three with so much to see!
